      "post_content": "One of my favourite cards in terms of function. It changes the rules, demanding you build around it.  \n  \n[Delaying Shield](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Delaying Shield) is one of the best cards to use with this, and [Death's Shadow](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Death's Shadow)? Instant beatstick.",
