    {
      "id": "PopularPost196238",
      "post_content": "Very, very fun card, extremely flavourful. You become a lich! Here are some cool synergies with other cards...\n  \n[Reapy in Kind](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Reapy in Kind), [Reverse the Sands](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Reverse the Sands) or [Mirror Universe](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Mirror Universe): kills your opponent(s) instantly or during next upkeep;\n  \n[Magus of the Mirror](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Magus of the Mirror): Same as above but much slower and subject to removal;\n  \n[Healing Salve](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Healing Salve): becomes an [Ancestral Recall](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Ancestral Recall)!\n  \n[Children of Korlis](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Children of Korlis): Sacrifice them to turn you play Lich to draw 20 cards!\n  \n[Transcendance](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Transcendance): Just a funny mechanic of \"discard a permanent and draw 2\" for each damage you take;\n  \n[Illusion of Grandeur](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Illusion of Grandeur): Draw 20 cards without the drawback;\n  \n[Elixir of Immortality](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Elixir of Immortality): Shuffle your graveyard in your library to avoid decking yourself with all this card draw, draw 5 cards;\n  \n[Death's Shadow](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Death's Shadow): Put these four 13/13 beatsticks on the boa... [(see all)](javascript:void(0);)",
      "posted_by": "Curious_Homarid",
      "html": "<div class=\"post evenItem\" id=\"PopularPost196238\" style=\"background-color: rgba(255,255,255,0.08);\">\n<span class=\"postContent\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl02_post\">Very, very fun card, extremely flavourful. You become a lich! Here are some cool synergies with other cards...\r<br/><a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Reapy in Kind\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Reapy in Kind\">Reapy in Kind</a>, <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Reverse the Sands\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Reverse the Sands\">Reverse the Sands</a> or <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Mirror Universe\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Mirror Universe\">Mirror Universe</a>: kills your opponent(s) instantly or during next upkeep; \r<br/><a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Magus of the Mirror\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Magus of the Mirror\">Magus of the Mirror</a>: Same as above but much slower and subject to removal; \r<br/><a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Healing Salve\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Healing Salve\">Healing Salve</a>: becomes an <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Ancestral Recall\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Ancestral Recall\">Ancestral Recall</a>!\r<br/><a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Children of Korlis\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Children of Korlis\">Children of Korlis</a>: Sacrifice them to turn you play Lich to draw 20 cards!\r<br/><a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Transcendance\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Transcendance\">Transcendance</a>: Just a funny mechanic of \"discard a permanent and draw 2\" for each damage you take; \r<br/><a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Illusion of Grandeur\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Illusion of Grandeur\">Illusion of Grandeur</a>: Draw 20 cards without the drawback; \r<br/><a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Elixir of Immortality\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Elixir of Immortality\">Elixir of Immortality</a>: Shuffle your graveyard in your library to avoid decking yourself with all this card draw, draw 5 cards; \r<br/><a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Death's Shadow\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Death's Shadow\">Death's Shadow</a>: Put these four 13/13 beatsticks on the boa... <a href=\"javascript:void(0);\" onclick=\"ExpandPost(event, this, 196238)\">(see all)</a></span>\n<div class=\"postDetails\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl02_postDetails\" style=\"padding-top: 5px;\">\n<div class=\"reportAbuse\">\n<a href=\"../../Classes/Controls/#\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl02_reportAbuseLink\" onclick=\"HandleReportPost(this, '196238'); return false;\">\r\n                                    Report Abuse</a>\u00a0\u00a0\r\n                                    \r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postedBy\">\r\n                                Posted By: \r\n                                <span id=\"PostedBy71743\">Curious_Homarid</span>\r\n                                (9/17/2011 4:19:42 AM)\r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postRating\">\n<div class=\"postRatingLabel\">\r\n                                    Rating:\u00a0\r\n                                </div>\n<div style=\"float: left;\">\n<div class=\"starRating\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl02_postRating_starRating\"><img alt=\"0.5\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/LeftSolidSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"1.0\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/RightSolidSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"1.5\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/LeftSolidSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"2.0\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/RightSolidSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"2.5\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/LeftSolidSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"3.0\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/RightSolidSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"3.5\" src=\"../../Images/