    {
      "id": "PopularPost246564",
      "post_content": "Okay, so I decided to try some of the Magus of the Mirror and Mirror Universe tricks that I've heard of with this on MTGO and I just want you guys to know that it doesn't actually work. I noticed that when it came around to my upkeep that I was not aloud to sac Magus or Mirror universe. Confused I decided to try to find why and it turns out that if you can't gain life (Lichs draw effect) you can't exchange life totals with a player who has a higher life total. =/ Oh well.",
      "posted_by": "YariMatthews",
      "html": "<div class=\"post oddItem\" id=\"PopularPost246564\">\n<span class=\"postContent\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl05_post\">Okay, so I decided to try some of the Magus of the Mirror and Mirror Universe tricks that I've heard of with this on MTGO and I just want you guys to know that it doesn't actually work. I noticed that when it came around to my upkeep that I was not aloud to sac Magus or Mirror universe. Confused I decided to try to find why and it turns out that if you can't gain life (Lichs draw effect) you can't exchange life totals with a player who has a higher life total. =/ Oh well.</span>\n<div class=\"postDetails\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl05_postDetails\" style=\"padding-top: 5px;\">\n<div class=\"reportAbuse\">\n<a href=\"http://wizards.custhelp.com/cgi-bin/wizards.cfg/php/enduser/ask.php?p_prods=522,706,739&amp;p_cats=\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl05_reportAbuseLink\" onclick=\"HandleReportPost(this, '246564'); return false;\">\r\n                                    Report Abuse</a>\u00a0\u00a0\r\n                                \r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postedBy\">\r\n                                Posted By: \r\n                                <span id=\"PostedBy18378\">YariMatthews</span>\r\n                                (5/17/2012 4:31:11 PM)\r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postRating\">\n<div class=\"postRatingLabel\">\r\n                                    Rating:\u00a0\r\n                                </div>\n<div style=\"float: left;\">\n<div class=\"starRating\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl05_postRating_starRating\"><img alt=\"0.5\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/LeftSolidSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"1.0\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/RightSolidSmall.png\"/>